    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/a5e75a4de17444f6e9f4c9e77d1496d2.avif?t=1759200287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras_big/a5e75a4de17444f6e9f4c9e77d1496d2.avif?t=1759200287 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>狐巫女翩翩起舞！有些许妖艳的搜寻怪异游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏规则十分简单！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首先请仔细观察狐巫女的舞蹈，并牢牢记住。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但请千万注意，不要因为沉迷于她的性感魅力而错过她的舞蹈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想回到你原来的世界，必须见证狐巫女的所有仪式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时会有『物之怪』干扰仪式，它们会假装成狐巫女，试图诱惑您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要被妖艳的狐之舞吸引而错过异变，以坚定的心守护仪式，揭示『物之怪』的真面目吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“其一！若认定确为妾身，便呼唤妾身之名！”</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“再一！若认为是仿冒妾身之物，便立刻揭穿骗局！”</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“但凡出错，仪式就会失败！”</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.poster.avif?t=1759200287\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.webm?t=1759200287\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/9d1df84054821c6568149ea52ca4348c.mp4?t=1759200287\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您的指正正确，『物之怪』会退去，灯笼将被点亮。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点亮所有的8盏灯笼，返回原来的世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >物之怪图鉴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被您识破『物之怪』瞬间中的各种姿态都会收藏在图鉴中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过重复仪式，来制作您独一无二艳丽的『物之怪图鉴』吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras/a43e5e4f04189bf9229feb58240b08b7.avif?t=1759200287\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034520/extras_big/a43e5e4f04189bf9229feb58240b08b7.avif?t=1759200287 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >＜Cast＞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Fox Shrine Maiden(CV:Maaya Uchida)</p>",
